overview.longBusinessSummary: Beacon Financial Corporation operates as the holding company for Beacon Bank & Trust that provides various banking solutions in New England and New York, the United States. The company accepts various deposit products. It also provides commercial, retail, and commercial real estate loans. In addition, the company offers equipment financing, SBA lending, and private wealth services; and cash management, and on-line and mobile banking services. Further, it is involved in the securities investment activities. The company was founded in 1871 and is headquartered in Boston, Massachusetts.
